post_text:
Harriet Tubman Essay Question-Grades 3-8
Answer the following question in at least 3 paragraphs of your own words. Feel free to use examples from Harriet Tubman's life that you have learned in school, in books or reliable websites. Top essays will receive an award and go on a special field trip!

A hero is a person, who in the face of danger, shows great bravery and strength. Harriet Tubman is often described as a great American Hero. Would you consider Tubman a hero? Why or why not?

Answer this questing in at least 3 paragraphs of your own words. Feel free to use examples from Harriet Tubman's life that you have learned at school, in books or reliable websites.
